定位置','Vertical Buttons'=>'直向按鈕','AddToAny &quot;floating&quot; share buttons stay in a fixed position even when the user scrolls.'=>'即使使用者捲動畫面，AddToAny 的浮動分享按鈕也會停駐於畫面的固定位置。','Most sites should not use this option. By default, AddToAny loads asynchronously and most efficiently. Since many visitors will have AddToAny cached in their browser already, serving AddToAny locally from your site will be slower for those visitors. If local caching is enabled, be sure to set far future cache/expires headers for image files in your <code>uploads/addtoany</code> directory.'=>'請注意，絕大多數的網站不需要啟用這項設定。依照預設，AddToAny 會以非同步及最有效率的方式載入。由於許多網站訪客會將 AddToAny 快取至他們所使用的瀏覽器中，因此提供這個網站伺服器本機的 AddToAny 快取會比網站訪客的快取還慢。如果伺服器本機的快取已啟用，請務必為 <code>uploads/addtoany</code> 目錄中的圖片檔案設定保留期限夠長的快取/到期標頭。','Cache AddToAny locally with daily cache updates'=>'每日更新伺服器本機的 AddToAny 快取','Specify the URL of the directory containing your custom icons. For example, a URL of <code>//example.com/blog/uploads/addtoany/icons/custom/</code> containing <code>facebook.png</code> and <code>twitter.png</code>. Be sure that custom icon filenames match the icon filenames in <code>plugins/add-to-any/icons</code>. For AddToAny\'s Universal Button, select Image URL and specify the URL of your AddToAny universal share icon (<a href="#" onclick="document.getElementsByName(\'A2A_SHARE_SAVE_button_custom\')[0].focus();return false">above</a>).'=>'請指定儲存自訂圖示的目錄網址。舉例來說，<code>facebook.png</code> 及 <code>twitter.png</code> 儲存於網址 <code>//example.com/blog/uploads/addtoany/icons/custom/</code> 中。請注意，自訂圖示檔案名稱與 <code>plugins/add-to-any/icons</code> 中的圖示檔案名稱必須相符。針對 AddToAny 的通用按鈕，請在<a href="#" onclick="document.getElementsByName(\'A2A_SHARE_SAVE_button_custom\')[0].focus();return false">上方</a>設定 AddToAny 通用按鈕圖示的圖片網址。','Filename extension'=>'檔案名稱的副檔名','Use custom icons. URL:'=>'使用自訂圖示。圖示網址:','Advanced Options'=>'進階設定','Advanced users should explore AddToAny\'s <a href="https://www.addtoany.com/buttons/customize/wordpress" target="_blank">additional opt